1.Create a function to calculate price_range(low, medium, high) of each product. If price<=70 indicate as low, upto 105 indicate as medium, and above as high.

i/p
-----
mysql> create function p_price(price int) returns varchar(20)
    -> deterministic
    -> begin
    ->  declare amt varchar(20);
    -> if price<=70 then set amt="low";
    -> elseif(price>=70 and price<=105) then set amt="medium";
    -> elseif price>105 then set amt="high";
    -> end if;
    -> return(amt);
    -> end
    -> //

